12
00:00:31,360 --> 00:00:36,040
♫ ...into that same song that your heart knows so well. And let it hold its meaning. ♫

13
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:38,340
What are you filming?

14
00:00:38,340 --> 00:00:40,690
The message I'm going to send to him.

15
